        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3201006253" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2993093584567700002">This book was SO LONG that I honestly can’t rate it. It was sooooo winding and sooo beautiful. I am really stuck on the ethics of telling other people’s stories, Agee is so obsessed with the fact that he can’t give a full picture of the sharecroppers’ lives he ends up reducing them to just his characterizations. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


