              <span id="reviewTextContainer2174073560" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer5543424272904296138">I made it page 100 then gave up. I simple could not understand what the author was trying to say. I realized the book was potentially a difficult read based upon feedback from other readers, however I found the prologue to be well written and thought provoking. That is why I did not give up until a quarter of the way through reading. </span>

